'''Felix Silla''' ([[January 11]], [[1930s#1937|1937]]&ndash;[[April 16]], [[2021]])<ref name="Death" /> was a stuntman who played the role of an [[Unidentified Ewok (hang glider) 1|unnamed Ewok]] flying a hang-glider in [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Star Wars'': Episode VI ''Return of the Jedi'']].<ref name="CIVOPAGL">{{WebCite|url=http://officialpix.com/OPX/Celebrities.html|text=Celebration IV Autograph HQ|work=officialpix.com|archivedate=20071015144459}}</ref>

